                    <div class="span12">
                        <h1>Non-deployable directive to help Army work toward more 'lethal' force</h1>
                        <p class="small">By Joe Lacdan, Army News Service<span>November 16, 2018</span></p>
                        <section class="alt-social-bar">
  <ul>
        <li class="social-button-sm twitter-button">
            <a rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.army.mil%2Farticle%2F213757%2Fnon_deployable_directive_to_help_army_work_toward_more_lethal_force&amp;text=Non-deployable%20directive%20to%20help%20Army%20work%20toward%20more%20%27lethal%27%20force"><span>Share on Twitter</span></a>
